<hymn_number>39</hymn_number>
<title>Ei Tandawk Tai</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa'n ka gitloh tanin,
 Lei ah albang A vai:
 Gilo hing taklote guolin,
 Thing ah a thawk sak ui.

[V2]
 Aw hinna Lal thiengtho tak chun,
 Kei di'n A thuok zo tai;
 Thihchana lungkhamna thuokin,
 Eihaw ei tandawk tai.

[V3]
 2. Hukdampa'n &quot;Ka dang a chak hi&quot;
 Ti a kiko lai khan;
 Mipi sang tamtak lak akhan,
 A pie nuom a um puou.

[V4]
 3. A lampi chu thil zel leuhing
 Kalvari tang tieng in,
 &quot;Lalpa ka hun zui ngam puou hi&quot;
 A gingte'n a tiu ui.

[V5]
 4. A lungkham A thavaih bang khan,
 Panpih a ngai zing hi;
 A deih bang thil hih zel dingin,
 Ka theihna a tawm ngal.</lyrics>
</song>